ygData.messageBody:
I started in mistmoore at 19 and leveled there till 27, from there i went
to cazic and fought in the tower and tae groups for a few levels, then did
the occasional upper zig when i got high enough (great safe exp up there),
left cazic at 35 and went to east karana killing guards till 48 then east
freeport guards till 50.. hope this helps you if you get stuck :)

Fetko, lvl 49 wizzie, Mith Marr
Sporklania, lvl 19 bard, Mith Marr

Brad Fetkovich
